trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of child controls in a table layout container.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av underordnede kontroller i en beholder for oppsett av tabellen.

trans-unit.source: The TableLayoutControlCollection class represents the collection of all the child controls in a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen TableLayoutControlCollection representerer samlingen av alle underordnede kontroller i en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>

trans-unit.source: This collection is exposed by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.Controls%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel> class.
trans-unit.target: Denne samlingen er utsatt <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.Controls%2A>for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>klasse.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.Controls%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can manage and individually manipulate members of the table layout panel through the TableLayoutControlCollection exposed by <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.Controls%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan administrere og endre individuelt medlemmer av tabellen oppsettet panelet via TableLayoutControlCollection eksponert i <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.Controls%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.Controls%2A>

trans-unit.source: The TableLayoutControlCollection class is a minor specialization of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ControlCollection> base class.
trans-unit.target: Klassen TableLayoutControlCollection er en underordnet spesialvariant av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ControlCollection>base klasse.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ControlCollection>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutControlCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutControlCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Generally, the application programmer will not directly create instances of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutControlCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis opprettes i applikasjonen programmer ikke direkte forekomster av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutControlCollection>klassen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutControlCollection>

trans-unit.source: Instead, a reference to an existing <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutControlCollection> is returned by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.Controls%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: I stedet en referanse til en eksisterende <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutControlCollection>er returnert av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.Controls%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.Controls%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutControlCollection>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel"></xref> control that contains the control collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel"> </xref> kontroll som inneholder samlingen for kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified control to the collection and positions it at the specified cell.
trans-unit.target: Legger til den angitte kontrollen til samlingen og plasseres på den angitte cellen.

trans-unit.source: With Add, you can specify the cell position of `control`.
trans-unit.target: Med Legg til, kan du angi celle posisjonen for `control`.

trans-unit.source: You can assign `control` to a specific cell by providing both the `column` and `row` parameters, or you can specify only the column or row value and let the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.LayoutEngine%2A> place `control` at the next open cell.
trans-unit.target: Du kan tilordne `control` til et bestemt ved å angi begge den `column` og `row` parametere, eller du kan angi bare kolonne- eller -verdi og la det <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.LayoutEngine%2A>plassere `control` på den neste åpne cellen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.LayoutEngine%2A>

trans-unit.source: This is known as letting the control *flow* to its position in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel> control.
trans-unit.target: Dette er kjent som å la kontrollen *flyten* til plassering i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>

trans-unit.source: Set `column` to -1 if you want `control` to occupy a fixed row position.
trans-unit.target: Angi `column` til-1 Hvis du vil `control` skal ha en fast posisjon.

trans-unit.source: Set `row` to -1 if you want `control` to occupy a fixed column position.
trans-unit.target: Angi `row` til-1 Hvis du vil `control` skal ha en fast kolonne posisjon.

trans-unit.source: If neither `column` nor `row` is -1, `control` will be added at the absolute position given by (`column`, `row`).
trans-unit.target: Hvis verken `column` eller `row` er -1, `control` legges til i den absolutte plasseringen angitt av (`column`, `row`).

trans-unit.source: If you set both `column` and `row` to -1, `control` will flow to the first open position, with the specific flow behavior defined by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.GrowStyle%2A?displayProperty=fullName> value.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir både `column` og `row` til-1, `control` flyter til den første open posisjonen med bestemte flyten virkemåten er definert av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.GrowStyle%2A?displayProperty=fullName>verdi.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.GrowStyle%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: This is equivalent to using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ControlCollection.Add%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Dette er det samme til ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ControlCollection.Add%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ControlCollection.Add%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: To get to the actual current position of a control, use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.GetPositionFromControl%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Gå til faktiske gjeldende posisjon til en kontroll ved bruk av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.GetPositionFromControl%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metode.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.GetPositionFromControl%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: This method takes into account the entire <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel> control state, including column or row spanning and when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.LayoutEngine%2A?displayProperty=fullName> has placed a control with its `Column` and `Row` properties set to -1.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden tar hensyn til hele <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>kontrollen tilstand, inkludert kolonne eller rad dekker og når den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.LayoutEngine%2A?displayProperty=fullName>har plassert en kontroll med den `Column` og `Row` egenskaper som er angitt til-1.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.LayoutEngine%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>

trans-unit.source: The control to add.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen for å legge til.

trans-unit.source: The column in which `control` will be placed.
trans-unit.target: Kolonnen der `control` skal plasseres.

trans-unit.source: The row in which `control` will be placed.
trans-unit.target: Raden der `control` skal plasseres.

trans-unit.source: Either column or row is less than -1.
trans-unit.target: Either column or row is less than -1.

trans-unit.source: Gets the parent <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel"></xref> that contains the controls in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter overordnet <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel"> </xref> som inneholder kontroller i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutControlCollection.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er angitt av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutControlCollection.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutControlCollection.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel"></xref> that contains the controls in the current collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel"> </xref> som inneholder kontroller i gjeldende samling.
